                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 168.) I received information and took the prisoner—he said he had a half-sovereign from the prosecutor, and lost it going to get change, that he meant to bring half-a-crown on the Mon<lb></lb>day, but did not like till he got the whole of it.</p>
